SUMMARY:Dungeons n' Drafts at Montclair Brewery
DESCRIPTION:The world’s greatest roleplaying game returns to Montclair Brewery! A Dungeon Master will be guiding players on their adventure so anyone with any experience level is welcome to join! It’s the perfect occasion for seasoned players and newcomers to come together. Let our flavorful brews influence the path you choose\, and enjoy a 10% discount offered to players during every event. \nGet your tickets while they’re still available! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
