SUMMARY:The Jist live at Montclair Brewery
DESCRIPTION:The Jist is an 8 piece powerhouse party band pushing a high energy dance flavor into funk\, rock\, & soul. Featuring a low blasting horn section\, dancefloor slamming latin percussion\, and a seamless set list of favorites and originals – they keep the vibes hot all night long. This NJ based group brings the groove\, and they certainly bring the party. Get the Jist? \n$5 cover charge per person that goes directly to the artists. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
