SUMMARY:Matcha Tea Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:The Japanese tea ceremony offers a quiet space to reconnect with the present moment. It’s a practice deeply rooted in centuries of tradition\, that is so much more than just quickly whisking some powder and water together. It’s an intentional process that elevate a simple beverage into a truly meaningful experience. In this hands-on workshop\, you won’t just taste premium matcha; you will learn the “why” behind every movement. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
