SUMMARY:Easter Sunday Prix-Fixe Menu
DESCRIPTION:🌷✨ Hop into Easter Sunday with us! ✨🌷\nCelebrate the day in style with a delicious three-course prix-fixe experience for $100 per person 🥂🍽️ \nGather your friends and family\, indulge in amazing flavors\, and make it a holiday to remember—we can’t wait to celebrate with you! 💐 \n$50 booking fee required at reservation (applied to your final bill) \nReserve your table now—this is one you don’t want to miss! 🐣💛 \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
