SUMMARY:2-for-1 TWOsdays
DESCRIPTION:Every 1st Tuesday of the month\, your day pass = entry for TWO. \nThat means you and a buddy can cowork\, jam\, and caffeinate together for just $30. \nNo codes. No awkward signup hoops. Just great vibes\, great company & a great deal. \nWork vibes + friend energy + saving money = a very good Tuesday. \nFAQs\nDo we have to arrive at the same time?\nNope — but there is one key rule. \nThe first person (Friend One) must be physically in the space and checked in. \nWhen the second person (Friend Two) arrives\, they’ll tell us Friend One’s name at the front desk and we’ll check them in as their buddy. \nNone of this\, like\, “My friend is coming later\, they’re the one who’ll pay” stuff. \nWhat if Friend One is a member?\nSame deal – the member needs to be in the space and checked in for their buddy to join them. \nCan you split the cost between me and my buddy?\nSure\, if you’re both here at the same time. Otherwise Venmo or Zelle comes in handy for Person 1 to get paid by Person 2 in that instance. \nCan I buy my day pass in advance?\nAbsolutely – and we encourage it!\nYou can grab a day pass ahead of time right here. \nThat said\, if you’re more of a just show up person\, that works too! Just come in with your credit card and your friendly neighborhood RecRoom team member will process your pass and get you set up. \nThat’s it. Simple\, flexible\, and easy to keep doing month after month. Maybe you want to put it as a recurring appointment on your calendar? #hinthint #notsubtle \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/2-for-1-twosdays-2/
LOCATION:RecRoom\, 1 Lackawanna Plaza\, Ste. 6\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community
